list.title: AME DEO DEMO Add LayerZero tokens
list.description: Stargate should become a hub for LayerZero assets (OFT tokens). Stargate should enable OFT tokens as an option for users, allowing a wider variety of tokens able to be bridged through Stargate. This will result in users having a singular easy destination to move many tokens cross chain allowing the protocol to also capture more long tail token flow without the need for more STG emissions.
